.TH "dma_request_chan" 9 "dma_request_chan" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
dma_request_chan \- try to allocate an exclusive slave channel
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "struct dma_chan *" dma_request_chan
.BI "(struct device *dev "  ","
.BI "const char *name "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "dev" 12
pointer to client device structure
.IP "name" 12
slave channel name
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Returns pointer to appropriate DMA channel on success or an error pointer.
